SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4392
A bill to make, supplement, and adjust appropriations for
certain capital outlay projects and the department of natural
resources for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2025; to provide
for expenditure of the appropriations; and to prescribe certain
conditions for the appropriations.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
